&control
    calculation = 'scf',
    prefix = 'CuO_bulk',
    outdir = './tmp',
    pseudo_dir = './SSSP', 
/
&system
    ibrav = 0,
    nat = 4,
    ntyp = 2,
    ecutwfc = 90,
    ecutrho = 720,
    occupations = 'smearing',
    smearing = 'mp',
    degauss = 0.02,
    nspin = 2,
    starting_magnetization(1) = 0.5,   ! Cu（假设 type 1 是 Cu）
    starting_magnetization(2) = 0.0,   ! O
/
&electrons
    conv_thr = 1.0d-8,
    mixing_beta = 0.3,
    electron_maxstep = 200,
/

CELL_PARAMETERS angstrom
 5.146719750  -0.270125090   0.524493504
-0.238899328   2.902259740  -0.097382859
-0.031694249  -0.162875833   2.967937934

ATOMIC_SPECIES
Cu  63.546  Cu.pbe-dn-kjpaw_psl.1.0.0.UPF
O   15.999  O.pbe-n-kjpaw_psl.0.1.UPF

ATOMIC_POSITIONS crystal
Cu               0.2520630330        0.1320998275        0.0599513446
Cu               0.7510497918        0.6294564926        0.5700610546
O                0.9935998122        0.5684716994        0.0077222773
O                0.5082873631        0.6649719805        0.1122653235

K_POINTS automatic
6 6 6 0 0 0


HUBBARD (ortho-atomic)
U Cu-3d 5.0